<br>
Phinny requires at most 2 groups (55 - 60) but thats not a HUGE deal since others need him to.<br>
<br>
Rottgrime require groups but this is an in and out raid.  Not too bad.<br>
<br>
The Torch from CoM, I got it MQ'd but it's not hard to get people to do reavers.<br>
<br>
Feather Cloak, i have a friend that is going to MQ it.  This is a major pain too.  I camped that zone for well over 24 hours alone killing every thing.  The few times the hourse spawned a druid would kill it and annouce it.. pissed me off.  If you can get a ranger or 2 to help you though it might not be that bad... Maybe a few hours if you are lucky.<br>
<br>
Crown of Mastery, who ever came up with this idea is a shmuck.  At the very least crowns should be a common drop on island 7, maybe a rare drop on the first island.  That way a  mage not in a uber guild has a shot at least.  They could leave it as it is though and put ragefire on the final island.. peeps would be in Air every day.<br>
<br>
The Staff of Elemental Mastery:Earth shoud also drop in Hole.  It is an under used zone (just like Air).  It makes more sense there anyway... just stick down at the bottom with that wretched guy. <p><TABLE><TR><TD>
