he Epic Quest Sucks...let's face it</span><hr size=1> A week ago I would have been in total agreement with this post.  I still feel for you, and all mages.  Our quest is niether easy or highly desired by guilds.   We need drops from mobs with days for spawn timers and even they they won't even the drop.<br>
